508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WhenWeWereYoung2025-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/WhenWeWereYoung2025-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/when-we-were-young">《当我们年轻的时候》2025 年</a>的阵容已经发布，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/panic-at-the-disco">《惊慌》的迅速重聚！ The Disco</a>于 2023 年解散。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/how-when-we-were-young-went-from-emo-fyre-fest-to-a-euphoric-pop-punk-party-3336793">《当我们年轻时》如何从“情绪狂欢节”转变为欢快的流行朋克派对</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（10 月 29 日），电影节与众多顶级人物分享了 2025 年海报，其中包括 Panic！与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/weezer">Weezer</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-offspring">The Offspring</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/knocked-loose">Knocked Loose</a>等一起。</p><p>为了庆祝其成立 20 周年，《恐慌！》 At The Disco 将完整表演他们的首张专辑《A Fever You Can&#39;t Sweat Out》，以及“其他一些你最喜欢的 Panic!”。 At The Disco 歌曲”，乐队在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBtzPLtup5-/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>帖子中宣布。</p><p>恐慌的改革！后硬核乐队 Letlive 并不是明年音乐节上唯一的重聚。正如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jason-aalon-butler-speaks-out-on-the-anniversary-of-letlive-and-teases-reissue-and-reunion-tour-3619080">主唱 Jason Aalon Butler 在今年早些时候透露的</a>那样，作为“适当”告别巡演的一部分，乐队已被添加到其阵容中，其他乐队还有 Never Shout Never、Jack&#39;s Mannequin 和 The Cab。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-gaslight-anthem">Gaslight Anthem</a>将于 2022 年重聚后也在音乐节上表演。</p><p>与此同时，《When We Were Young》中还安排了一系列流行朋克表演，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/all-time-low">《All Time Low》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yellowcard">《Yellowcard》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-used">《Theused</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-plan">《Simple Plan》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taking-back-sunday">《Taking Back Sunday》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mayday-parade">《Mayday Parade》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-story-so-far">《The Story So Far》</a> 。较重的方面，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alexisonfire">Alexisonfire</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-nine-kills">Ice Nine Kills</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motionless-in-white">Motionless In White</a> 、Kublai Khan TX、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-religion">Bad Religion</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beartooth">Beartooth</a>和 Loathe。</p><p>预售将于本周五（11 月 1 日）上午 10 点（太平洋时间）开始 -<a href="http://whenwewereyoungfestival.com">在此处</a>注册以接收访问代码以便加入。请参阅下面的完整阵容。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBtyxWgPUIC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="eve